<F P=100> Economic &amp; Agricultural </F>
<H3> <TI>   Trade, Production Statistics Issued for 1993 </TI></H3>
<H4>   Export Figures To Latin America </H4>
<F P=102> HK0802104394 Beijing CEI Database in English 8 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> HK0802104394 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing CEI Database </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing (CEIS) -- Following is a list showing the 
value of China's exports to Latin American countries and regions 
in January-December 1993, released by the General Administration 
of Customs: 


------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|                         |1-12/1993                |1-12/1992 (Unit: 10,000  | 
|                         |                         |U.S. dollars)            | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Country and region       |Exports                  |Exports                  | 
