<F P=102>  OW0303012494 Beijing XINHUA in English 0041 GMT 3 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW0303012494 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Kitakyushu, Japan, March 2 (XINHUA) -- Chinese 
Vice-Premier Zhu Rongji today visited Yasukawa Electrical Corp., 
a leading Japanese robot manufacturer located in this industrial 
city in southwestern Japan. 
  Zhu inspected a computerized robot production and research 
facility called Motorman Center, where he saw robots arranging 
flowers, assembling robots and writing. 
  The Chinese vice-premier said he hoped that Yasukawa would 
expand its cooperation with China, including technology transfer. 
  Zhu is here on his last leg of a nine-day Japan trip. 
Earlier, he visited Toto Ltd., a major sanitary wear maker in 
Japan. 

