<H3> <TI>   XINHUA Kills Item on Emulating Lei Feng Forum </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW0203114194 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 0842 
GMT 2 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> OW0203114194 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Chinese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [By correspondents Tang Fen (3282 1164) and Zhang Jiabin </F>
(4545 0163 2430); XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese at 0955 GMT 
on 2 March transmits a service message killing the following 
item] 
  [Text] Beijing, 2 Mar (XINHUA) -- A national forum of 
militia representatives outstanding in emulating Lei Feng was 
held in Beijing yesterday. The representatives summed up and 
exchanged experiences of launching the campaign to learn from 
Lei Feng under the new circumstances of expediting reform and 
opening up and establishing a socialist market economic 
structure. They pledged to more conscientiously take the lead 
in learning from Lei Feng and to bring into full play the role 
of militiamen in building two civilizations. 
  Taking part in the forum were advanced representatives, who 
take the initiative to implement the party's policy encouraging 
efforts to become prosperous and, after becoming better off, 
remember the state and collectives by leading others onto the 
road of common prosperity; who seek neither fame nor wealth and 
work selflessly at ordinary posts; who enthusiastically render 
services for others and set a good example in fostering new 
socialist customs and habits; who risk life to protect the life 
and property of people; and who safeguard motherland unification 
and national unity and make active contributions to promoting 
stability and development of the frontier region. 
  They will attend special report meetings on their advanced 
deeds in the capital. 

</TEXT>

