<H3> <TI>   Li Lanqing Speaks on Educational Reform, Development </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW0203142694 Beijing XINHUA in English 1355 GMT 2 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW0203142694 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, March 2 (XINHUA) -- Vice-Premier Li Lanqing 
today spoke to a meeting of 800 teachers and students held at 
the People's University of China on current affairs and 
government policy. 
  Those present came from all the universities in Beijing. 
  On educational reform and development, Li noted that China 
will further promote the development of scientific, 
technological and educational services to accelerate 
modernization. 

</TEXT>

