Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, March 3 (XINHUA) -- Chinese Vice-Premier Li 
Lanqing met Moeen A. Qureshi, former senior vice-president of 
the World Bank here today. 
  Qureshi, a long-time senior vice-president of the World 
Bank, 
now chairs the Asian Fund which is jointly financed by the 
