<H3> <TI>   XINHUA Cites U.S. Official on Constructive Relations </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW0403063194 Beijing XINHUA in English 0618 GMT 4 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW0403063194 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Washington, March 3 (XINHUA) -- A senior U.S. 
official said here today that the United States hopes to build a 
more constructive relationship with China. 
  Assistant Secretary of State Winston Lord told reporters at 
a 
news briefing that "the China-U.S. relationship is extremely 
